<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/903295-can-i-read-this-book-before-all-creatures">Can I read this book before All Creatures Great and Small? Or is there a sequence that needs to be followed?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_903295'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F38743.All_Things_Bright_and_Beautiful">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/903295-can-i-read-this-book-before-all-creatures">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/903295-can-i-read-this-book-before-all-creatures">See all 3 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/12901314-priscilla"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1470621000i/12901314._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/12901314-priscilla">Priscilla</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
Each chapter is a different story, but you get to know the characters and their background better if you read the books in sequence.
</span>
</div>
</div>
