<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/935154-do-you-have-to-read-the-first-ones-to-read">do you have to read the first ones to read this ?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_935154'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F38743.All_Things_Bright_and_Beautiful">like</a></span>

