        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1589300067" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5019334195171817592">I first read this book 30 years ago, and I this week I listened to it in the car on a long road trip. These books are amazing and so funny. I spent half the drive going down the road laughing out loud in my car (and sometimes even tearing up a bit). <br/><br/>When I was a child I was sure I wanted to be a veterinarian. I think these books probably made a huge contribution that. I never did become a vet, but I still love the books.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


